    <h1>Lose It! Alternative<br><span class="green">for Men Over 40</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Lose It! is a well-designed weight loss app. If weight loss is your goal, it works. If muscle preservation through protein is your goal, it's solving the wrong problem entirely.</p>
    <p style="color:#6ee7a0;font-family:'Plus Jakarta Sans',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1rem;margin-top:1rem;">The goal isn't to eat less. It's to eat more of the right thing.</p>
    <p style="color:#9ca3af;font-size:0.97rem;margin-top:0.5rem;">Most men over 40 aren't even measuring the one number that matters. And this app doesn't make that number obvious.</p>
