          <div class="friction-item">
            <span class="friction-badge">FRICTION</span>
            <div class="friction-body"><strong>Data in the cloud.</strong> Lose It! requires an account and stores data on their servers. For the 40+ demographic — which surveys consistently show has higher privacy concerns about health data — an app that keeps everything local is meaningfully different from one that doesn't.</div>
